# Data — raw downloads and large intermediate artifacts are not committed.
# Exceptions below are the small (~2.4MB total), verified files app.py needs
# to run on Streamlit Community Cloud (see docs/DEPLOYMENT.md).
#
# IMPORTANT: several raw files are DUA-gated (Synapse: BCM-DMAS, proteomics) —
# these must NEVER be published to a public repo regardless of size, since
# redistribution would likely violate the data-use terms agreed to when
# downloading them. The blanket rules below cover data/raw/ (their proper
# home) AND loose files dropped directly in data/ (their initial download
# landing spot before being sorted) — both must stay excluded.
data/*.csv
data/*.zip
data/*.txt
data/*.xlsx
data/raw/*
data/interim/*
data/processed/*
!data/**/.gitkeep
!data/processed/grm.npz
!data/processed/benchmark_accuracy.csv
!data/processed/gsea_convergent_pathways.csv
!data/processed/convergence_leave_one_out.csv
!data/processed/shared_biology_convergent_genes.csv
!data/processed/gwas_adj_genes_*.csv
!data/processed/qtt_top_*.csv
!data/processed/pathway_assoc_*.csv

# Models — exceptions are the small v1.0/v1.1 artifacts the deployed app needs.
models/trained/*.pkl
!models/trained/drophenopredict_v1.0.json
!models/trained/drophenopredict_v1.0_targets.npz
!models/trained/drophenopredict_v1.1.json
!models/trained/drophenopredict_v1.1_kernels.npz

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local tooling config (not project content)
.claude/
